data.description: End Unit townhome on the lake with a whole house water system, solar panels and has a downstairs master suite and a 2 car garage.  Spacious eat in kitchen, appliances included with breakfast bar, opens to dining room and family room with sliders to a patio.  Fenced yard with oasis:  hot tub, pergola and dry bar..  The Master suite offers lake view, a double sink vanity and walk in closet. Upstairs loft overlooks the family room and entry foyer. Great space for an office or library.   The 2 additional bedrooms have walk in closets and share a bath. The gated community offers a club house and fitness center, resort style swimming pool overlooking the lakes with a soothing fountain. (light fixtures not included)  This complex is less than 1/2 mile from Hightower Park Beach!
